 through my sobs.

“Oh, une sale affaire—a beastly business: changed clothes with a man and killed him. But appease yourself, my friend, it is not only in Germany that murderers exist, we have our Landrus, thank heaven, so that you are not alone. Calmezvous, it is all nerves, the local water acts beautifully upon the nerves—or more exactly, upon the stomach, ce qui revient au même, d’ailleurs.”

He went on with his patter for a little while and then rose. I returned the handkerchief w